    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained macaroni</strong> to the pan with the leek béchamel sauce</p><p>Add the <strong>remaining grated cheese</strong>, season with <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up until the cheese has meltedl</p>",
